Name: Smasher and the Will o' the Thiccs
About the game: Golf meets girth! Slam your way through walls, and swell your way through stages, vacuuming the Will o' the Thiccs as you go! 9 Main Story Levels Over 60 extra objectives Blueberry Inflation Mode to test your skills while constantly swelling up! 2 Bonus levels to enjoy and have fun with! Almost 400 unlockable Player Skins Set the skins for the NPCs Redesigned and refreshed levels More to come with free updates!
